steps.name: I count elements having css selector "header nav .site-nav-left ul li" and store count in variable
I enter "<ADMIN_USER>" into input field having id "ember8"
I enter "<ADMIN_PASSWORD>" into input field having id "ember10"
I click on element having id "ember12"
I click on element having css selector "a[href*='design']"
I click on element having css selector "#settings-navigation > .sortable-objects > div:last-child button.gh-blognav-delete"
I click on element having css selector "main button:first-child"
I compare elements having css selector "header nav .site-nav-left ul li" with stored variable minus 1
